{
  "stem": "20609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, no one transports.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "October-- I think November, no more transports.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we found out the Russians already-- we-- we still don't know what's going on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So one day, we got a transport of about 40 kids, young kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So they go-- they're-- they're-- they're really in bad shape, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So I knew somebody in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they bring them over to the hospital and the hospital had facilities to take showers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Kids didn't want to go in the shower room.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We still don't know what the hell was going on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "So now they clean these kids up, they-- you know, and they get shipped out again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We never knew where they went.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And strange things happening.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "All of a sudden, it's now the beginning of '45 now, you know, like January, February.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All of a sudden, an order comes down if somebody wants to volunteer for Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're making up a transport of 500 people to go to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Bullshit, right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody volunteers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All of a sudden, some of us says, screw it, let's go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let's-- let's put our name down. what-- what-- you know, what can happen, right?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We volunteered for barracks building at one time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they wanted volunteers to go out to build barracks for the German Army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just to get out of camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were all turned down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Danish people, the Danish guys, were turned down.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now we were onto-- some of us volunteered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know if I did it or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We volunteered for to go on that trip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We get turned down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they finally had to grab 500 people, and sure enough that transport went to-- went to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This was when the war was almost over, right.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
